ws its opening price, not its value; nPrice reports how many listings each price is based on. This is a sample, not a census: boxes and packs are sampled with dedicated queries, so the box/pack/card split is not a market share figure — compare each category against its own history, not against the others.","updated":"2026-07-20"}
